### User

* _id
* username: `String`
* password: `String`

### Categories

* _id
* name: `String`  (eg. 'Bailleurs Sociaux')
* slug: `String`  (eg. 'bailleurs-sociaux')

### Article

* _id
* section: `String` [ 'project', 'lab' ]
* title: `String`
* shortDescription: `String`
* createdAt: `Date`
* categories: `Array of Strings` (Array of categories ids)
* content: `String` (stringify HTML)
